{"tid":2150894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被女朋友話我掛住打機","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T17:03:20.000Z","uid":53092,"like":2,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d478a6cfcaf5cbe51dd17cb838f6031a843d531c","tid":2150894,"uid":53092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊左兩個月左右，大家係打機識<br />\n<br />\n近排被女朋友話我每日收工之後排住打機唔理佢...<br />\n講講下仲話覺得自己被冷落，話覺得我唔需要佢咁...<br />\n講到好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n其實我打機中間都有間中覆下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每晚訓前一個鐘都會同佢wts<br />\n近排追緊一隻game就話我冷落佢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我同女朋友本身都係打機識<br />\n我放工打下機輕鬆下都有問題咩<br />\n係唔係我女朋友太大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人有類似經歷，一齊圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a413de855ab2c2e439e327645bb174df9254f928","tid":2150894,"uid":194326,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"咁打你女朋友囉"},{"pid":"20e9085d94af5b65826537d4c2f0aa9181c049de","tid":2150894,"uid":38904,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"感建分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f8928e449950c24a440f894dbd304eaeb1ee6c","tid":2150894,"uid":114062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"我幫你陪下條女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7f532172a83e1c1f2de995c39c98972411151d","tid":2150894,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"追緊咩game"},{"pid":"6b7a1c7eddc89cbe1cdd39745b52b090685a59c9","tid":2150894,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"買多左蘋果既手足 唔好齋擺屋企 當派報紙咁直頭擺去隔離鄰舍門口！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2150861\" data-auto-li